(10, 189, 'chexton', 'chris@getvero.com', '', '165.228.217.140', '2012-10-29 21:52:00', '2012-10-29 21:52:00', 'Thanks Emello, we''ve just released part 2 of the series of 3 posts, in case you missed it! http://blog.getvero.com/pump-up-your-ltv-with-email-remarketing-increase-your-customer-lifespan-part-2-of-3/', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):695725699', '', 9, 0),
(11, 4, 'Stephen Brooks', 'stephen.brooks@microcadsoftware.com', '', '81.151.138.20', '2012-12-03 13:09:00', '2012-12-03 13:09:00', 'Great post. The cheat sheet is really helpful too. There is way too much to take in when you first learn email marketing and this is nice and simple.', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):726014133', '', 0, 0),
