(38, 532, 'Maria', 'maria@fitnessreloaded.com', '', '50.131.41.139', '2013-03-07 17:57:00', '2013-03-07 17:57:00', 'Hi Chris!\n\n\nYou mentioned that your own conversion rate is 8%. Do you mean that the sign-up form on the sidebar does that? Or, are you referring to something else?\n\n\nAlso, why did you choose 7 e-mails over a month? Did you run any tests before you came down to this?\n\n\nThank you for your article! ;)', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):822123454', '', 0, 0),
(39, 532, 'chexton', 'chris@getvero.com', '', '121.210.168.190', '2013-03-10 04:30:00', '2013-03-10 04:30:00', 'Hi Maria, thanks for the comments. \n\nCorrect - 8% of people who start my ''educational course'' go on to sign up for a free trial. \n\nSeven emails was a ballpark figure. I am meaning to test a few different timings but, due to the size of the list, wouldn''t yet be able to report meaningful findings just yet! Based on my own experience I felt twice a week would be the maximum frequency I''d like to hear from a business (assuming they''re sharing good content) so went with that!', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):824460112', '', 38, 0),
