(104, 742, 'starshiplove', 'vb12dogs@yahoo.com', '', '174.44.87.86', '2013-06-03 16:07:00', '2013-06-03 16:07:00', 'Great article. Email is less hyped up now that social media has become such a big part of the marketplace. There are hundreds of companies listed at http://www.buyfacebookfansreviews.com alone and this has become a bigger part of the market. But there''s no doubt that email is still a super important part of how any company needs to interact with their customers. Especially in certain niches, particularly in B2B, email is how business purchasing decisions get made and it''s vital to interact with prospects through there. Without this attention and emphasis, a lot of businesses will be much worse off.', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):917761717', '', 0, 0),
(105, 860, 'SalesPortal', 'khetrapalsaurabh@gmail.com', 'http://www.salesportal.com/', '76.118.6.221', '2013-06-14 15:31:00', '2013-06-14 15:31:00', 'Email is a great way to keep in touch with your customer base. The key is to figure out what they want to hear from you and how often! It''s very easy to do too little (and lose the connection) or too much (and annoy them into unsubscribing). There is not always a "right" way so what works best for you and your audience?', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):930722268', '', 0, 0),
