(154, 1076, 'Stevie Brooks', 'broox_z@hotmail.com', '', '86.174.78.6', '2013-10-24 13:19:00', '2013-10-24 13:19:00', 'Probably the best post I have seen yet. The problem I have is that what do you do if you know how to put the emails together but you are not experienced enough in a particular industry to provide your subscribers with useful information? Is it best to do research and then pretend you are an authority on the subject?', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):1095031697', '', 0, 0),
