(207, 1204, 'Cyril Gaillard', 'cyril@melvia.com.au', '', '123.243.50.82', '2013-12-05 20:11:00', '2013-12-05 20:11:00', 'Great article!  A quick question: when trying to grow a SAAS, how would you decide between free trial (Vero, Kissmetrics) or freemium (Mixpanel, Dropbox)?', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):1152024160', '', 0, 0),
