(289, 1153, 'Anupam Bonanthaya', 'anupam.bonanthaya@gmail.com', 'http://customertestimonials.wordpress.com', '122.178.230.11', '2014-03-10 10:22:00', '2014-03-10 10:22:00', 'Chris, this is useful stats ! do you have insights if the images are that of customers ? it will be interesting to see how these numbers change on using customer photos (testimonials) ....', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):1278434725', '', 0, 0),
