(422, 2743, 'Christos Vareloglou', 'christosvare@gmail.com', 'http://thedigitalrookie.com/', '5.54.82.255', '2014-05-28 19:06:00', '2014-05-28 19:06:00', 'Aaron and Bree i agree that GIFs are an innovative way of increasing your CTR. Despite that general fact, i''m working as a Project Leader for the E-mail Marketing in an Online Travel Agency, called Travelplanet24.com(Our global brand name is "Tripsta") and after making twice an A/B test between a JPEG and a GIF, i saw that there wasn''t any difference between their CTRs. \nDo you have any statistics to share from your tests?\n\n\nGreetings from Greece,\nChristos\n\n\nP.S. You can always reach me at my e-mail: cvareloglou@travelplanet24.gr', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):1408825903', '', 409, 0),
