(454, 3096, 'Jimmy Daly', 'runjimdaly@gmail.com', 'http://blog.getvero.com', '68.63.199.168', '2014-06-18 21:45:00', '2014-06-18 21:45:00', 'They''ve done a hell of job building a great brand but I don''t know much about the community efforts. I see a blog and some social activity but it''s not overly impressive.', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):1442550911', '', 452, 0),
