(462, 3096, 'Jimmy Daly', 'runjimdaly@gmail.com', 'http://blog.getvero.com', '68.63.199.168', '2014-06-19 16:36:00', '2014-06-19 16:36:00', 'Ah, gotcha. I recommend starting with a blog, even if it''s a free, personal site. It''s a place to share your thoughts and, as long as there is a comments section, it can be the seedling of a community.', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):1444120054', '', 461, 0),
