(467, 2444, 'Vicky', 'victoriafarwellla@yahoo.com', '', '216.14.19.83', '2014-06-26 23:40:00', '2014-06-26 23:40:00', 'Nice article. Does personalizing the company name resonate as ''sweetly'' as using the owner''s first name? Sometimes we want to highlight the benefit for the business by naming it, which is ultimately the benefit of the owner ... but makes the message more about the business entity than the individual. think it works?', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):1456357612', '', 0, 0),
