(478, 3167, 'Karl Philip Lund', 'kp@kingspoint.no', 'http://tribes.no', '46.29.216.106', '2014-07-02 08:37:00', '2014-07-02 08:37:00', 'Awesome post. One note about the Chase bank example. Phishing is a huge problem for banks. Thats probably why they dont include links in their e-mails. Its a security thing......', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):1464657835', '', 0, 0),
