(532, 3767, 'Jimmy Daly', 'runjimdaly@gmail.com', 'http://blog.getvero.com', '68.63.199.168', '2014-08-14 14:50:00', '2014-08-14 14:50:00', 'We''ve analyzed a ton of emails (more than 100 million) sent by Vero users and have found one key thing: it *really* depends on the business and the location of the subscriber. Vero users are all over the world so it''s nearly impossible to nail down a "perfect" time to send an email. Some people have a lot of success with weekend emailing because of the decreased volume on Saturday and Sunday while others find that their subscribers are most active on Mondays. I wish I had a more concrete answer but it''s something that each business needs to optimize individually.\n\n\nWe''ll be publishing all of the data from our analysis very soon :)', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):1542546788', '', 531, 0),
