(571, 3538, 'Email Monks', 'ravi@emailmonks.net', 'http://www.emailmonks.com/', '27.109.9.66', '2014-09-10 13:13:00', '2014-09-10 13:13:00', 'Thank\n  you Jimmy for the interesting article! However the email volume may go up\n  because of the increased number of email accounts and marketers trying to\n  leverage the situation. The marketers can stay abreast of such challenges by\n  following best practices for 2014. We have them elaborated on: http://www.emailmonks.com/blog/email-marketing/5-email-marketing-resolutions-you-ought-to-religiously-follow-in-2014/', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.77):1582482013', '', 0, 0),
