(670, 4686, 'Jimmy Daly', 'runjimdaly@gmail.com', 'http://blog.getvero.com', '68.63.199.168', '2014-11-07 14:42:00', '2014-11-07 14:42:00', 'Good question. Seems to be roughly the same 20% range in my experience.', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):1681335049', '', 668, 0),
(671, 4686, 'Jimmy Daly', 'runjimdaly@gmail.com', 'http://blog.getvero.com', '68.63.199.168', '2014-11-07 14:43:00', '2014-11-07 14:43:00', 'You raise a good point. It makes a lot of sense for Airbnb because it''s likely their customers are "in the know". Might not be such a good idea for AARP. :)', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):1681336780', '', 666, 0),
(672, 4630, 'David (ProfitPursuits.com)', 'david@profitpursuits.com', 'http://profitpursuits.com/', '50.106.45.203', '2014-11-07 23:41:00', '2014-11-07 23:41:00', 'Awesome post Jimmy! You are doing a killer job at Vero with all of this useful content.  Plus, the tool looks awesome.  I''ll have to give it a try.', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):1682206077', '', 0, 0),
(673, 4686, 'chexton', 'chris@getvero.com', '', '67.180.208.36', '2014-11-08 01:31:00', '2014-11-08 01:31:00', 'Great question Enguerrand, I don''t actually know which platform they use (BuiltWith.com is sometimes helpful though...)\n\n\nRight now we don''t do predictive analytics, but we DO collect the data. Predictive analytics in the future...but right now we give you a sweet platform to create your own segments, automate campaigns against those and then test the campaigns (A/B test subjects, templates, copy, etc.)\n\n\nTwo main forms of data you can collect: user properties/demographics  i.e. you pass us data like age, location, etc.  and user actions you''ve defined like ''Viewed product'', etc. (exactly like Mixpanel or similar). \n\n\nYou can pump in data via Javascript or the API, it all matches up nicely in Vero.\n\n\nOur recommendation is to track each action in your customer lifecycle, from say ''Signed up'' to ''Used feature X'' to ''Used feature Y'' to ''Subscribed to plan'' to ''Charged credit card'' and so on.\n\n\nOur integrations with MP + Google Analytics are via UTM codes, which works well for the analytics side of things.\n\n\nIf you have any other specific questions, keep asking here or email me at chrish@getvero.com. If I''m not mistaken, you might even be in Sydney? If so, be happy to meet up there personally!', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):1682319503', '', 664, 0),
