(703, 4752, 'Jaina', 'jaina.mistry84@gmail.com', '', '37.131.1.137', '2014-11-20 07:33:00', '2014-11-20 07:33:00', 'The email''s got a great sense of hierarchy in the design too, with the typography. The key titles are clear, so even if you glossed over the email, you''ll get a good picture what it''s about and if it''s something you''re interested in. \n\nNot a huge fan of the big grey block at the bottom. I understand why they did it, but think it messes with the finesse of the rest of the email.', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):1702770154', '', 0, 0),
