(841, 4686, 'Jimmy Daly', 'runjimdaly@gmail.com', 'http://blog.getvero.com', '68.63.199.168', '2014-11-06 08:42:00', '2014-11-06 16:42:00', 'Hi Andrew - Vero and Mixpanel are apples and oranges. Mixpanel tracks actions as well but Vero allows you to trigger emails as a result of those actions. They could be used in tandem but they largely accomplish different goals.', 0, '1', '', '', 834, 0),
