(1025, 4341, 'Swadhin Agrawal', 'swadhin2005@gmail.com', 'http://www.DigitalGYD.com', '112.79.38.201', '2015-02-05 05:49:00', '2015-02-05 05:49:00', 'Hi Jimmy got over here from the backlinko blog and stumbling every possible page of your blog to imbibe some awesome tips. Its great your content is getting great traction and awesome mentions. I am also a fan of the "epic content" strategy. \n\nI am not here to linkdrop but would like to draw your attention to one of my posts that in a way got great response. link: http://www.digitalgyd.com/blogging-ideas-inspiration/\n\nNow, That I still could not promote the heck out of this deserving post could you give me some tips to get posts placed on top link round-ups like yours n buffer. I am coming up with another post on 600+ tips to get something done. I would be grateful if you get help me out in time so that I would get the new post enough exposure.\nThanks :)', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):1835947840', '', 0, 0),
