(1078, 5464, 'Bill', 'bill.lee789@gmail.com', '', '116.100.38.214', '2015-02-24 07:46:00', '2015-02-24 07:46:00', 'Awesome post with great details Jimmy! You are always making every post worthy with your effort and incredible insight. \n\nI would greatly appreciate it if you kindly give me some idea of what GetVero can do? (1) can you do something similar to theTripAdvisors Email Marketing? Note: We do not need Email #13, Email #15, Email #16, Email # 19, Email #20. (2) To send Email #8 and Email #18, how complex is the Facebook Integration?  (3) To use GetVero for the above things, do we need\nto build any feature into our platform/website? Or GetVero can do it all?\n\nFYI: We are a startup project in Vietnam (in developing phase), building a website based on the Udemy concept but it''s much\nsimpler with phase 1 target for only Vietnam market. As such, your advice will be really valuable to us.\n\nThanks,\nBill', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):1872240496', '', 0, 0),
