(1084, 5464, 'Jimmy Daly', 'runjimdaly@gmail.com', 'http://blog.getvero.com', '107.2.12.250', '2015-02-24 16:29:00', '2015-02-24 16:29:00', 'Yes, Vero can handle all of this - even integration with an API to pull in external data. Check out all the features here:\n\nhttps://www.getvero.com/features/\n\n\n\nA trial is really the best way to kick the tires and see what you think.', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):1872876332', '', 1079, 0),
(1085, 5464, 'Jimmy Daly', 'runjimdaly@gmail.com', 'http://blog.getvero.com', '107.2.12.250', '2015-02-24 16:31:00', '2015-02-24 16:31:00', 'Bill - Thanks so much for the compliment!\n\n\nVero can handle all of these emails, including complex ones like #20. Vero users can pull data from an API, meaning you can personalize emails with just about anything.\n\n\nAs for integrating your app with Facebook, that''s a separate challenge. If you can do it though, you can use the data in your emails with Vero.\n\n\nCheck out the trial, sounds like it''s just what you need: https://www.getvero.com/features/\n\n\nShoot me an email if you have any other questions: jimmy at getvero dot com', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):1872881248', '', 1078, 0),
