(1091, 4686, 'Justin Hamilton', 'justin@jhamilton.me', '', '66.31.139.250', '2015-02-25 02:53:00', '2015-02-25 02:53:00', '@Paul J, separate topic, but interested in hearing your thoughts...\n\n\nBuilding and iterating on complicated communication logic (mix of transactional and time-based, multi-channel) is making it more difficult to visually map the customer journey. I just started using OmniGraffle to diagram, but organizing the flows in a "pretty" way is challenging.\n\n\nAny experience with building out a nice visualization of email stream flow/logic? Tips/examples? Appreciate any insight!', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):1874043939', '', 690, 0),
