(1096, 5464, 'Aivaras Ko', 'bliudaz@gmail.com', '', '82.135.195.164', '2015-02-26 13:17:00', '2015-02-26 13:17:00', 'On my way...\n\n\nBut feature page lacks details about:\n1. Email builder. So I assume its HTML only\n2. Inside email analytics (clicks, CTR, etc). Assume none.\n3. Subscribtion Forms. Assume you have none.\n\nLack of info certainly leads to Free Trial.\nOR, pushes prospect to look for another email client.\n\nSince you''re the one (best?) in transaction+behavior email niche, got to put some patients and go for Trial.\n\nAnyway, your blog posts are amazing. Keep up the good work. \nAnd as Athif said - your posts certainly births new ideas for our to-do lists ;) Thanks!', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):1876557976', '', 1084, 0),
