(1298, 5009, 'Brendan', 'bquinn@oneclickventures.com', 'http://www.mathdrquinn.github.io', '23.25.52.237', '2015-06-17 15:11:00', '2015-06-17 15:11:00', 'Thanks for posting. Just because these emails seem transactional in nature, does that make them qualify as transactional legally?  I felt that point wasn''t make clear.', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):2083943753', '', 0, 0),
