(1332, 6559, 'jones19876', 'crsh1976@gmail.com', '', '161.69.67.20', '2015-07-10 14:51:00', '2015-07-10 14:51:00', 'I love Evernote, but as a user who signs up and uses a lot of these services nowadays, the amount of emails I get is a complete turn-off; I understand the point, I understand they''re supposed to be helpful, but what comes off (to me) as nothing more than nagging reminders often leads me to find the off switch asap.\n\n\nAgain, it''s a great case study on paper, in a user context it''s not always the most useful thing - Evernote is not the only service a typical user is signed up to, and don''t expect it to be either.\n\nAllow me to tweak what I want to hear about and allow me to tweak when I feel is a decent timeframe to be reminded about it.', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):2128616515', '', 0, 0),
