(1350, 5955, 'Andy Thompson', 'andythompsonts@gmail.com', '', '43.226.7.34', '2015-07-24 05:34:00', '2015-07-24 05:34:00', 'Hello, interesting article and lots of great blogs to look at and read. Thanks. :)\n\nTry marketing on Facebook.\nCheck our site if you have the time: <a href="http://www.troopsocial.com/" rel="nofollow">Troopsocial</a>', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):2154310295', '', 0, 0),
