(1352, 6746, 'NiftyImages', 'social@niftyimages.com', '', '23.30.37.221', '2015-07-27 17:57:00', '2015-07-27 17:57:00', 'Thanks Jimmy and Jen for the great write up!  I wanted to put another test out there.  \n\nOur company helps businesses personalize emails and weve found\nsimilar results expressed in this blog post. While personalizing email can be\nas trivial as Dear Jimmy Daly, you can also take it to the next level like\nthis:\n\nhttps://www.niftyimages.com/ex/h/4dr/cdr?name=Jimmy+Daly\n\nor something like\n\nhttps://www.niftyimages.com/ex/h/4td/ctd?name=Jimmy+Daly\n\nHopefully this comment does come off as too spammy. Just thought I would introduce\nanother level of personalizing emails for those willing to test.', 0, '1', 'Disqus/1.1(2.83):2159702311', '', 0, 0),
