(53, 3, '2014-07-03 02:55:42', '2014-07-03 02:55:42', '<p style="color: #222222;">Vero is different from other email service providers because it is built around<b>customer actions.</b>Using the Vero API, you track what customers do on your website<b>after you get their email.</b>You can see this data in realtime in Vero and use it to create detailed segments and send personalized campaigns.</p>\n<iframe class="wistia_embed" style="color: #222222;" src="http://fast.wistia.net/embed/iframe/ek6q63w3xf" name="wistia_embed" width="810" height="506" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe>\n<h3 style="color: #222222;">Installing the library and identify code</h3>\n<p style="color: #222222;">Copy the following code onto<b>every page</b>of your website, just before the<b>&lt;/head&gt;</b>tag.</p>\n<p style="color: #222222;">Copy the following code onto every page of your wesite where you<b>know the current visitor''s email address,</b>just before the<b>&lt;/body&gt;</b>tag.</p>\n\n<h3 style="color: #222222;">Testing it worked</h3>\n<p style="color: #222222;">To check if you have installed these two sections of Javascript correctly, open your website in a new tab, login and you browse around. If you return to Vero and head to the<a style="color: #00c3e4;" href="http://app.getvero.com/people">Customers</a>tab you''ll be able to see your email show up.<b>Success!</b>Your first subscriber in Vero.</p>\n<p style="color: #222222;"></p>', 'Install the Vero Library (3 minutes)', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '43-autosave-v1', '', '', '2014-07-03 02:55:42', '2014-07-03 02:55:42', '', 43, 'http://localhost:8888/?p=53', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(54, 3, '2014-07-03 03:11:09', '2014-07-03 03:11:09', 'Christmas, Easter, Halloween, Thanksgiving and other holidays are laden with folklore and culture you can use to personalize and enhance your marketing efforts.By keeping your communication timely and in theme with the season you can <strong>create new opportunities</strong> to market to your customers.\r\n\r\nEmail marketing is a great channel for communication during these events but sometimes its tricky to know what emails you can send.The <strong>ten strategies </strong>included in this eBook will help you prepare for the upcoming holiday season and ensure you get results.\r\n\r\nEven if you implement <strong>just one</strong> of these strategies youll certainly make a difference to your bottom line next holiday.', '10 Email Marketing Ideas To Triple Your Sales These Holidays', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', '10-email-marketing-ideas-to-triple-your-sales-these-holidays', '', '', '2014-07-03 06:32:52', '2014-07-03 06:32:52', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?post_type=resources&#038;p=54', 0, 'resources', '', 0),
