(142, 3, '2014-07-15 05:33:54', '2014-07-15 05:33:54', '<h2>What''s this guide about?</h2>\r\nWe''ve written <strong>The</strong> <strong>Ultimate Guide To Successful Email Marketing</strong> to give you a framework for setting up your email marketing from scratch and optimizing your campaigns over time.\r\n\r\nWe''ve pulled together the steps in this guide based on the <strong>highly s</strong><strong>egmented and targeted email marketing campaigns</strong> we''ve seen our customers send at <a href="http://www.getvero.com">Vero</a>, the campaigns we''ve tested ourselves and market-leading examples we''ve seen out in the wild.\r\n\r\nWhen I got started with email marketing at Vero, I always wished there had been someone to teach me many of the lessons I''ve learned from trial and error. This guide is the guide I wanted for myself. With over 10,000 words, advice from 15+ experts and countless examples this guide will generate new ideas and give you the firepower to make your email marketing a success.\r\n<h2>Who should use this guide?</h2>\r\nThis guide is written with two groups of marketers in mind:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><strong>Those new to email marketing:</strong> If you''ve never done any email marketing this guide will give you step-by-step instructions on how to get started <strong>and</strong> what to do next so that your campaigns actually <em>get the results</em> that you want.</li>\r\n	<li><strong>Those whose campaigns need a boost:</strong> If you''ve been running email marketing campaigns for a while but aren''t seeing the ROI that you <strong>want</strong>, Chapters 2-7 will give you practical advice that you can use to review your email marketing strategy and improve your campaigns to ensure you <strong>do</strong> achieve your goals.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nAll of the chapters in this guide feature screenshots and examples that you can use for practical inspiration. The chapters cover everything from selecting an email service provider and strategising for your trigger-based campaigns to configuring your emails for maximum deliverability.\r\n\r\nWe also asked a bunch of experts to share their key words of wisdom on each chapter so you can learn from the best.\r\n\r\n<h2>Table of Contents</h2>\r\nHere''s an outline of what''s included in the guide:\r\n\r\n<div id="toc">[toc_chapter color="blue" number="1" title="Your Basic Setup" image="http://blog.getvero.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/1_11.png" link="/guides/email-marketing-guide/getting-started/" intro="Understanding how to get started with email marketing a challenge. Do you need an email service provider? Which service provider is right for you? Getting your head around templates and the basic terminology takes time. This chapter will walk you through everything you need to get started with email marketing today." cta="Take me to Chapter 1"][toc_chapter color="green" number="2" title="Getting Subscribers" link="/guides/email-marketing-guide/get-subscribers/ " cta="Take me to chapter 2" image="http://blog.getvero.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/2_21.png" intro="The first step to any email marketing campaign is getting subscribers. Without subscribers you''ll never get a chance to learn and grow as an email marketer. This chapter shows you <strong>multiple ways you can grow your subscriber base</strong>, whether you''re just starting or already have millions of customers."][toc_chapter color="gray-blue" number="3" title="Your First Campaign Strategy" image="http://blog.getvero.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/3_32.png" intro="Once you''ve got subscribers, it''s time to email them. In this chapter you learn the difference between newsletters and trigger-based email campaigns and we <strong>provide you a strategy</strong> to plan your campaigns for maximum effect." link="/guides/email-marketing-guide/campaign-strategy/" cta="Take me to chapter 3"][toc_chapter color="orange" number="4" title="Creating Killer Content" image="http://blog.getvero.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/3_12.png" intro="Writing great emails, as with any content, requires time and effort. There''s so much to think about, from the subject line to the body copy to the call to action. In this chapter we break down the <strong>three main components of any email marketing campaign</strong> and give you tips and tricks to write better emails." link="/guides/email-marketing-guide/creating-killer-content/" cta="Take me to chapter 4"][toc_chapter color="aqua" number="5" title="Tracking Your Results" image="http://blog.getvero.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/5_21.png" intro="If you''re not tracking your results then you are flying blind. Opens and clicks are important but <strong>conversions are the key.</strong> This chapter shows you how to track and interpret opens, clicks and conversions using your email and analytics tools." link="/guides/email-marketing-guide/tracking-email-metrics/" cta="Take me to chapter 5"][toc_chapter color="purple" number="6" title="Optimizing Email Campaigns" image="http://blog.getvero.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/4_11.png" intro="After you''ve come this far you''ll be successfully sending and tracking email marketing campaigns. The question you''ll ask yourself is<strong> how can I make these campaigns better?</strong> In this chapter we focus on how to optimize your campaigns and share examples of successful approaches to email conversion optimization." link="/guides/email-marketing-guide/optimize-email-campaigns/" cta="Take me to chapter 6"][toc_chapter color="red" number="7" title="Bonus Tips &amp; Tricks" image="http://blog.getvero.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/6_41.png" intro="The world of email marketing is full of intricacies. In this chapter we cover <strong>email deliverability</strong>, how to design <strong>responsive email templates</strong> and ways you can increase <strong>on-page</strong> subscription and conversion rates. Learn the ins and outs of some of the most detailed aspects of email marketing." link="/guides/email-marketing-guide/email-tips-tricks/" cta="Take me to chapter 7"]</div>', 'The Ultimate Guide To Successful Email Marketing', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'email-marketing-guide', '', '', '2015-05-11 01:18:46', '2015-05-11 01:18:46', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?post_type=guides&#038;p=142', 0, 'guides', '', 0),
