(2042, 3, '2014-11-12 17:58:55', '2014-11-12 17:58:55', '<h2>The Job</h2>\r\nOur Customer Success Manager will be dedicated to making the customer experience phenomenal. Making people happy should make you happy and anything less than perfection is unacceptable.\r\n\r\nOur Customer Success Manager will play two key roles:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Take complete ownership of customer support. Set the tone for customer interaction, manage incoming support tickets and work with our developers to squash bugs and improve the product.\r\n\r\nPatience and a relentlessly positive attitude are key.</li>\r\n	<li><p>Exceed customer expectations by onboarding new users and making sure existing customers are getting the maximum value from the product.</p></li>\r\n	<<p>Your proactive approach will delight customers and ensure a return on their email marketing investment.</p></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<strong>What else?</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>You have a working knowledge of HTML and Javascript.</li>\r\n	<li>You have worked in a customer-facing role at an online company.</li>\r\n	<li>You are willing and ready to chip in with marketing, content, sales and more.</li>\r\n	<li>You are energetic, passionate and ready to conquer to the world.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Customer Success Manager', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'customer-success-manager', '', '', '2014-11-13 00:17:23', '2014-11-13 00:17:23', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?post_type=jobs&#038;p=2042', 0, 'jobs', '', 0),
