(5045, 3, '2015-06-13 14:17:44', '2015-06-13 14:17:44', 'We''re not 100% there yet but we''ve been working on a few tweaks to ensure that when you edit a saved segment, you can be clear what Vero is doing.\r\n\r\nThis is the workflow you should expect:\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>You edit your segment.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>You are redirected to the Segments dashboard, and you should be able to find your segment and see a progress bar as it updates.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>You can''t edit a segment whilst it is calculating.</li>\r\n\r\n<li>Once calculated the Segments dashboard will show the up-to-date count of users in that segment.</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Improve the workflow around re-calculating segments', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'improve-the-workflow-around-re-calculating-segments', '', '', '2015-06-13 14:17:44', '2015-06-13 14:17:44', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/?post_type=product_updates&#038;p=5045', 0, 'product_updates', '', 0),
